		"description": "# üì° StapuBox API Postman Documentation\n\nThis documentation outlines the endpoints available in the **StapuBox** collection. All endpoints use `http://localhost:8080` as the base URL.\n\n## üèü Venue Management\n\n### 1\\. Fetch All Venues\n\n- **Method:** `GET`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/venues`\n- **Description:** Retrieves a list of all registered venues.\n    \n\n### 2\\. Create / Update Venue\n\n- **Method:** `POST`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/venues/upsert-venue`\n- JSON{ \"venueName\": \"GTS23\", \"sportId\": \"7031809\"}\n    \n\n### 3\\. Delete a Venue\n\n- **Method:** `POST`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/venues/delete-venue`\n- JSON{ \"pk\": \"Kp0jkQZme5\"}\n    \n\n---\n\n## üïí Time Slot Management\n\n### 1\\. Add Time Slot for Venue\n\n- **Method:** `POST`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/venues/{venuePk}/slots`\n- **Description:** Adds a booking window to a specific venue using its encrypted PK (e.g., `OL0WNXoQ82`).\n- JSON{ \"startTime\": \"2026-01-09 13:03:39\", \"endTime\": \"2026-01-19 13:03:39\"}\n    \n\n### 2\\. Search Available Venues\n\n- **Method:** `GET`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/venues/available`\n- **Description:** Finds available slots based on time range and sport category.\n- JSON{ \"startTime\": \"2026-01-09 13:03:39\", \"endTime\": \"2026-01-25 13:03:39\", \"venue\": { \"sportId\": \"7031809\" }}\n    \n\n---\n\n## üé´ Booking Logic\n\n### 1\\. Book a Slot\n\n- **Method:** `POST`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/bookings`\n- **Description:** Reserves a specific time slot using its encrypted PK.\n- JSON{ \"pk\": \"OGrWalZp2M\"}\n    \n\n### 2\\. Cancel a Booking\n\n- **Method:** `PUT`\n- **Endpoint:** `/api/bookings/{bookingPk}/cancel`\n- **Description:** Cancels an existing booking by its PK.\n    \n\n---\n\n## ü©∫ System Monitoring\n\n### 1\\. Actuator Health Check\n\n- **Method:** `GET`\n- **Endpoint:** `/actuator/health`\n- **Description:** Checks the application's overall health and database connection status.\n    \n\n---\n\n### **How to Use This Documentation**\n\n1. Ensure your application is running via `docker-compose up`.\n2. Import the `StapuBox.postman_collection.json` file directly into Postman.\n3. Ensure the Content-Type header is set to `application/json` for all POST/PUT requests.",
